/picbed.yoyolikescici.cn/uPic/iShot2021-04-12%2011.55.48.png)\r\n\r\n谢谢各位。", "content_rendered": "<p>坐标某双非一本，考研失利，准备二战。\n辅导员从开学初就督促我们找工作，并明示或暗示找不到工作影响你毕业。\n已经打过好几次电话催促我了，我说我要二战他说没有这个选项。\n今天辅导员又在院里大群里发布了要求找工作的信息。</p>\n<p>上网查了说是不允许这样做，但不清楚执行起来是否有余地。</p>\n<p>辅导员这样做？我要怎样在不影响毕业的前提下维护自己的权益？</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"http://picbed.yoyolikescici.cn/uPic/iShot2021-04-12%2011.55.48.png\"/></p>\n<p>谢谢各位。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1618199934, "replies": 51, "id": 770037}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_large.png?m=1614702882", "name": "nas", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_normal.png?m=1614702882", "title": "NAS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/nas", "topics": 368, "footer": "", "header": "关于网络存储设备的讨论", "title_alternative": "NAS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_mini.png?m=1614702882", "stars": 653, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 949, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"username": "cathedrel", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/53dfa28d1216eee3dea9ace91e696120?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/cathedrel", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1608838844, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/53dfa28d1216eee3dea9ace91e696120?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/53dfa28d1216eee3dea9ace91e696120?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 525457}, "last_reply_by": "froyobin", "last_touched": 1618278858, "title": "用 Pi 做 NAS 有没有什么槽点？？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/770153", "created": 1618222102, "content": "家里两个现成的硬件都有问题： \r\n\r\nv2ex.com/t/769624\r\n\r\nv2ex.com/t/749937\r\n\r\n采购新硬件的话要小要新，好像只有 Pi 之类的可以选择了，如果入手树莓派最新的 2G 版本的单单做个 NAS 够了吧？尤其传输速度上？？", "content_rendered": "<p>家里两个现成的硬件都有问题： </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://v2ex.com/t/769624\" rel=\"nofollow\">v