r\">fonts.googleapis.com</a>”这个域名的 ip 地址解析到一个只能在墙内访问而在墙外无法访问的 203 开头的北京谷歌的 ip 上面，使得我几乎无法正常打开所有使用了 Google Fonts 的网站，Google 是想做什么？", "last_modified": 1618220476, "replies": 43, "id": 770142}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1615112532", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1615112532", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 171370, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1615112532", "stars": 3204, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"username": "dzdh", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1683/7ebf/226307_mini.png?m=1584535572", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/dzdh", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1492349895, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1683/7ebf/226307_mini.png?m=1584535572", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1683/7ebf/226307_mini.png?m=1584535572", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 226307}, "last_reply_by": "dzdh", "last_touched": 1618278407, "title": "API 接口已经有 HTTPS 的前提下，为什么还需要签名机制？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/770172", "created": 1618228115, "content": "注意场景：\r\n\r\n- 服务端对服务端的接口，不是客户端对服务端的接口\r\n- 防止中间人可以 PINNED Pub Key，因此中间人攻击不在考虑范围内\r\n- 极端条件可以使用客户端证书\r\n\r\n综合以上三点。为什么在 Https 的保护下，还要额外做签名验证？\r\n\r\n主要疑问，如 stripe 的退款接口\r\n```\r\ncurl https://api.stripe.com/v1/refunds -u \"$密钥:\" -d charge=$charge_id\r\n```\r\n\r\n就可以发起一笔订单的退款或者扣款。按照某些论述的话，没有签名的 Stripe 岂不是非常危险？", "content_rendered": "<p>注意场景：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>服务端对服务端的接口，不是客户端对服务端的接口</li>\n<li>防止中间人可以 PINNED Pub Key，因此中间人攻击不在考虑范围内</li>\n<li>极端条件可以使用客户端证书</li>\n</ul>\n<p>综合以上三点。为什么在 Https 的保护下，还要额外做签名验证？</p>\n<p>主要疑问，如 stripe 的退款接口</p>\n<pre><code>curl https://api.stripe.com/v1/refunds -u \"$密钥:\" -d charge=$charge_id\n</code></pre>\n<p>就可以发起一笔订单的退款或者扣款。按照某些论述的话，没有签名的 Stripe 岂不是非常危险？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1618228115, "replies": 40, "id": 770172}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_large.png?m=1615111970", "name": "hardware", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_normal.png?m=1615111970", "title": "硬件", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/hardware", "topics": 3789, "footer": "", "header": "硬件发烧友的讨论节点", "title_alternative": "Hardware", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_mini.png?m=1615111970", "stars": 1755, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 52, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"username": "forbreak", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b8610989d38d6a55d04f88b483886b2c?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/forbreak", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1416391220, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b8610989d38d6a55d04f88b483886b2c?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b8610989d38d6a55d04f88b483886b2c?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 82516}, "last_reply_by": "newmlp", "last_touched": 1618253437, "title": "求推荐一台笔记本，不知道现在 windows 的触摸板做的怎么样，能不能做到不用鼠标直接用触摸板还很舒服。现在用的 13 款 mbp，习惯不用鼠标只用触摸板很舒服。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/770066", "created": 1618207224, "content": "如题，有没有用 windows 的不用鼠标只用触摸板的。是否能达到 mac 的体验。 旧电脑的性能太弱鸡了，不知道现在的 windows 纯用触摸板体验如何。比如最近很火的 yoga 14s 小新 pro  metabook 14 这种 。", "content_rendered": "如题，有没有用 windows 的不用鼠标只用触摸板的。是否能达到 mac 的体验。 旧电脑的性能太弱鸡了，不知道现在的 windows 纯用触摸板体验如何。比如最近很火的 yoga 14s 小新 pro  metabook 14 这种 。", "last_modified": 1618207224, "replies": 36, "id": 770066}]